race.comment: EPIC DESIRE (3) is yet to break through after three career starts. Managed to fill a minor placing at Saratoga (Dirt) two starts back when resuming before finishing fourth over 1710m at Saratoga (Turf) last start. Can break through in this suitable contest. BEHOLD THE KING (6) went forward and gave a great sight before finishing second last time out over 1710m at Colonial Downs (Turf). Facing a tougher assignment but he is up to the task. CHAMBERSVILLE (7) made his debut last start and was just fair in finishing seventh at Saratoga (Turf) over 1710m, beaten 4 lengths. Should do better this time around. SPECIAL ENVOY (2) is on debut. By Not This Time and is out of the Chad C Brown stable. Top-three chance.
